#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/storage.py:323
msgid ""
"The following unformatted or LDL DASDs have been detected on your system. "
"You can choose to format them now with dasdfmt or cancel to leave them "
"unformatted. Unformatted DASDs cannot be used during installation.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"ກວດພົບ DASD ທີ່ຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ຟໍແມັດ ຫຼື ເປັນ LDL ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນລະບົບຂອງທ່ານ. ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຟໍແມັດດຽວນີ້ດ້ວຍ "
"dasdfmt ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກເພື່ອປ່ອຍໃຫ້ຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ຟໍແມັດ. DASD ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຟໍແມັດຈະບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ໃນລະຫວ່າງການຕິດຕັ້ງ.\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/storage.py:330
msgid ""
"Warning: All storage changes made using the installer will be lost when you "
"choose to format.\n"
"\n"
"Proceed to run dasdfmt?\n"
msgstr ""
"ຄຳເຕືອນ: ການປ່ຽນແປງບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດທີ່ເຮັດຜ່ານຕົວຕິດຕັ້ງຈະສູນຫາຍເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກທີ່ຈະຟໍແມັດ.\n"
"\n"
"ດຳເນີນການແລ່ນ dasdfmt ຫຼືບໍ່?\n"

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/storage.py:339
msgid "This may take a moment."
msgstr "ອາດໃຊ້ເວລາຈັກໜ່ອຍ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/storage.py:355
msgid "Passphrase"
msgstr "ລະຫັດຜ່ານ"

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/storage.py:356
msgid ""
"Please provide a default LUKS passphrase for all devices you want to "
"encrypt. You will have to type it twice."
msgstr ""
"ກະລຸນາປ້ອນລະຫັດຜ່ານ LUKS ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນສຳລັບທຸກອຸປະກອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເຂົ້າລະຫັດ. ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງພິມມັນສອງຄັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/storage.py:447
