"Incorrectly specified origin of the snapshot. Use format \"VolGroup/LV-name\""
msgstr "ລະບຸຕົ້ນທາງຂອງສະແນບຊັອດບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຮູບແບບ \"VolGroup/LV-name\""

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:55
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have not defined a root partition (/), which is required for "
"installation of %s to continue."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດພາຕິຊັນຮາກ (root) (/), ເຊິ່ງຈຳເປັນສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ %s ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:60
#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/interactive/utils.py:428
msgid "You must create a new file system on the root device."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງສ້າງລະບົບໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່ເທິງອຸປະກອນຮາກ (root)."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:66
#, python-format
msgid "Your root partition must be on a device of type: %s."
msgstr "ພາທິຊັນ root ຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງອຸປະກອນປະເພດ: %s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:85
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The LDL DASD disk {name} ({busid}) cannot be used for the installation. "
"Please format it."
msgstr ""
"ດິສກ໌ LDL DASD {name} ({busid}) ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງໄດ້. ກະລຸນາຟໍແມັດມັນກ່ອນ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:107
#, python-format
msgid ""
"It is recommended to create a new file system on your %(mount)s partition."
msgstr "ຂໍແນະນຳໃຫ້ສ້າງລະບົບໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່ໃນພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:123
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is less than %(size)s which is lower than "
"recommended for a normal %(productName)s install."
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານນ້ອຍກວ່າ %(size)s ເຊິ່ງຕ່ຳກວ່າຂະໜາດທີ່ແນະນຳສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ %"
"(productName)s ປົກກະຕິ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:131
#, python-format
msgid "Your %(mount)s partition size is lower than required %(size)s."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດພາທິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານຕ່ຳກວ່າ %(size)s ທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:151
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is too small for %(format)s formatting (allowable "
"size is %(minSize)s to %(maxSize)s)"
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານນ້ອຍເກີນໄປສຳລັບການຟໍແມັດ %(format)s (ຂະໜາດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ %"
"(minSize)s ຫາ %(maxSize)s)"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:157
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is too large for %(format)s formatting (allowable "
"size is %(minSize)s to %(maxSize)s)"
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານໃຫຍ່ເກີນໄປສຳລັບການຟໍແມັດ %(format)s (ຂະໜາດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ %"
"(minSize)s ຫາ %(maxSize)s)"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:175
msgid "No valid boot loader target device found. See below for details."
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບອຸປະກອນເປົ້າໝາຍສຳລັບຕົວໂຫຼດບູດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:188
msgid "You have not created a bootable partition."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ສ້າງພາຕິຊັນທີ່ສາມາດບູດໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:231
msgid ""
"Your BIOS-based system needs a special partition to boot from a GPT disk "
"label. To continue, please create a 1MiB 'biosboot' type partition on the {} "
"disk."
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບທີ່ໃຊ້ BIOS ຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງການພາທິຊັນພິເສດເພື່ອບູດຈາກດິສທີ່ມີປ້າຍກຳກັບ GPT. ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່, ກະລຸນ"
"າສ້າງພາທິຊັນປະເພດ 'biosboot' ຂະໜາດ 1MiB ເທິງດິສ {}."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:256
msgid ""
"The system will not be bootable. The firmware does not support XFS file "
"system features on the boot file system. Upgrade the firmware or change the "
"file system type."
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບຈະບໍ່ສາມາດບູດໄດ້. ເຟີມແວບໍ່ຮອງຮັບຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງລະບົບໄຟລ໌ XFS ໃນລະບົບໄຟລ໌ບູດ. ກະລຸນາອັບເກຣດເຟີມ"
"ແວ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນປະເພດລະບົບໄຟລ໌."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:314
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have not specified a swap partition. %(requiredMem)s of memory is "
"recommended to continue installation without a swap partition, but you only "
"have %(installedMem)s."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸພາຕິຊັນ swap. ແນະນຳໃຫ້ມີໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ %(requiredMem)s ເພື່ອສືບຕໍ່ການຕິດຕັ້ງໂດຍບໍ່ມີພາ"
"ຕິຊັນ swap, ແຕ່ທ່ານມີພຽງແຕ່ %(installedMem)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:321
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have not specified a swap partition. %(requiredMem)s of memory is "
"required to continue installation without a swap partition, but you only "
"have %(installedMem)s."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸພາຕິຊັນ swap. ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ %(requiredMem)s ເພື່ອສືບຕໍ່ການຕິດຕັ້ງໂດຍບໍ່ມີພ"
"າຕິຊັນ swap, ແຕ່ທ່ານມີພຽງແຕ່ %(installedMem)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:328
msgid ""
"A swap partition has not been specified. To significantly improve "
"performance for most installations, it is recommended to specify a swap "
"partition."
msgstr ""
"ຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດພາທິຊັນ swap. ເພື່ອເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບໃນການຕິດຕັ້ງສ່ວນໃຫຍ່, ຂໍແນະນຳໃຫ້ກຳນົດພາທິຊັນ swap."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:346
msgid ""
"At least one of your swap devices does not have a UUID, which is common in "
"swap space created using older versions of mkswap. These devices will be "
"referred to by device path in /etc/fstab, which is not ideal since device "
"paths can change under a variety of circumstances. "
msgstr ""
"ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໃນອຸປະກອນ swap ຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນບໍ່ມີ UUID, ເຊິ່ງເປັນເລື່ອງປົກກະຕິສຳລັບພື້ນທີ່ swap ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນມາໂ"
"ດຍໃຊ້ mkswap ລຸ້ນເກົ່າ. ອຸປະກອນເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກອ້າງອີງໂດຍເສັ້ນທາງອຸປະກອນ (device path) ໃນ /etc/"
"fstab, ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ເໝາະສົມປານໃດ ເພາະເສັ້ນທາງອຸປະກອນສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ໃນຫຼາຍສະຖານະການ. "

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:365
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This mount point is invalid. The %s directory must be on the / file system."
msgstr "ຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ນີ້ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ %s ຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງ/ລະບົບໄຟລ໌."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:381
#, python-format
msgid "Your %s must be on a separate partition or LV."
msgstr "%s ຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງພາທິຊັນ ຫຼື LV ທີ່ແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:398
#, python-format
msgid "The mount point %s must be on a linux file system."
msgstr "ຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ %s ຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງລະບົບໄຟລ໌ Linux."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:423
msgid ""
"The existing unlocked LUKS device {} cannot be used for the installation "
"without an encryption key specified for this device. Please, rescan the "
"storage."
msgstr ""
"ອຸປະກອນ LUKS {} ທີ່ປົດລັອກຢູ່ແລ້ວ ບໍ່ສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ໃນການຕິດຕັ້ງໄດ້ ໂດຍທີ່ບໍ່ມີການລະບຸລະຫັດການເຂົ້າລະຫັດສຳລັ"
"ບອຸປະກອນນີ້. ກະລຸນາສະແກນບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຄືນໃໝ່."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:444
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Encryption requested for LUKS device %s but no encryption key specified for "
"this device."
msgstr ""
"ມີການຮ້ອງຂໍການເຂົ້າລະຫັດສຳລັບອຸປະກອນ LUKS %s ແຕ່ບໍ່ມີການລະບຸລະຫັດການເຂົ້າລະຫັດສຳລັບອຸປະກອນນີ້."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:466
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The available memory is less than %(size)s which can be too small for LUKS2 "
"format. It may fail."
msgstr ""
"ໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳທີ່ມີຢູ່ແມ່ນໜ້ອຍກວ່າ %(size)s ເຊິ່ງອາດຈະໜ້ອຍເກີນໄປສຳລັບຮູບແບບ LUKS2. ມັນອາດຈະຫຼົ້ມເຫຼວ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:507
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%s is currently mounted and cannot be used for the installation. Please "
"unmount it and retry."
msgstr ""
"%s ຖືກເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ (mounted) ຢູ່ ແລະ ບໍ່ສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ໃນການຕິດຕັ້ງໄດ້. ກະລຸນາຍົກເລີກການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ "
"(unmount) ແລ້ວລອງໃໝ່."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:542
msgid ""
"Selected disks {} contain volume group '{}' that also uses further "
"unselected disks. You must select or de-select all these disks as a set."
msgstr ""
"ດິສທີ່ເລືອກ {} ປະກອບມີກຸ່ມວໍລຸມ (volume group) '{}' ທີ່ໃຊ້ດິສອື່ນໆທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກເລືອກນຳ. ທ່ານຕ້ອງເລືອກ "
"ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກການເລືອກດິສເຫຼົ່ານີ້ທັງໝົດເປັນຊຸດ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/snapshot/device.py:45
msgid "Snapshot: origin \"{}\" doesn't exist!"
msgstr "ແຊັບຊັອດ: ຕົ້ນສະບັບ \"{}\" ບໍ່ມີຢູ່!"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/snapshot/device.py:50
msgid ""
"Snapshot: origin \"{}\" of snapshot \"{}\" is not a valid thin LV device."
msgstr ""
"ແຊັບຊັອດ: ຕົ້ນສະບັບ \"{}\" ຂອງແຊັບຊັອດ \"{}\" ບໍ່ແມ່ນອຸປະກອນ thin LV ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/snapshot/device.py:56
msgid "Snapshot {} already exists."
msgstr "ແຊັບຊັອດ (Snapshot) {} ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:41
msgid "First sector of boot partition"
msgstr "ເຊັກເຕີທຳອິດຂອງພາທິຊັນບູດ"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:42
msgid "RAID Device"
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນ RAID"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:43
msgid "Master Boot Record"
msgstr "Master Boot Record"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:44
msgid "EFI System Partition"
msgstr "ພາທິຊັນລະບົບ EFI"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:45
msgid "PReP Boot Partition"
msgstr "ພາທິຊັນບູດ PReP"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:46
msgid "Apple EFI Boot Partition"
msgstr "ພາທິຊັນບູດ Apple EFI"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:47
msgid "Apple Bootstrap Partition"
msgstr "ພາທິຊັນ Apple Bootstrap"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:48
msgid "DASD"
msgstr "DASD"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:49
msgid "zFCP"
msgstr "zFCP"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:80
#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:386
msgid "You must include at least one disk as an install target."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາດິສຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໜ່ວຍເປັນເປົ້າໝາຍການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:154
msgid ""
"You must include at least one MBR- or GPT-formatted disk as an install "
"target."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ MBR ຫຼື GPT ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໜ່ວຍເປັນເປົ້າໝາຍການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:196
msgid ""
"For a UEFI installation, you must include an EFI System Partition on a GPT-"
"formatted disk, mounted at /boot/efi."
msgstr ""
"ສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງແບບ UEFI, ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາພາທິຊັນລະບົບ EFI ເທິງດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ GPT, ໂດຍເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ "
"(mount) ໄວ້ທີ່ /boot/efi."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:249
msgid ""
"For a UEFI installation, you must include a Linux HFS+ ESP on a GPT-"
"formatted disk, mounted at /boot/efi."
msgstr ""
"ສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງແບບ UEFI, ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາ Linux HFS+ ESP ເທິງດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ GPT, ໂດຍເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ "
"(mount) ໄວ້ທີ່ /boot/efi."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:315
msgid ""
"You must include a PReP Boot Partition within the first 4GiB of an MBR- or "
"GPT-formatted disk."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາພາທິຊັນບູດ PReP ພາຍໃນ 4GiB ທຳອິດຂອງດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ MBR ຫຼື GPT."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:354
msgid ""
"You must include an Apple Bootstrap Partition on an Apple Partition Map-"
"formatted disk."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາພາທິຊັນ Apple Bootstrap ເທິງດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ Apple Partition Map."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:404
msgid ""
"You must include at least one MBR- or DASD-formatted disk as an install "
"target."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ MBR ຫຼື DASD ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໜ່ວຍເປັນເປົ້າໝາຍການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:442
msgid "You must include at least one MBR-formatted disk as an install target."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ MBR ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໜ່ວຍເປັນເປົ້າໝາຍການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/bootloader.py:172
msgid "GRUB2 does not support installation to a partition."
msgstr "GRUB2 ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບການຕິດຕັ້ງລົງໃນພາທິຊັນ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/bootloader.py:179
msgid "GRUB2 encrypted password must be in grub.pbkdf2 format."
msgstr "ລະຫັດຜ່ານທີ່ເຂົ້າລະຫັດຂອງ GRUB2 ຕ້ອງຢູ່ໃນຮູບແບບ grub.pbkdf2."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/execution.py:146
msgid "No match found for given boot drive \"{}\"."
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກົງກັນສຳລັບໄດຣຟ໌ບູດ \"{}\" ທີ່ໃຫ້ມາ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/execution.py:150
msgid "More than one match found for given boot drive \"{}\"."
msgstr "ພົບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກົງກັນຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງອັນສຳລັບໄດຣຟ໌ບູດ \"{}\" ທີ່ໃຫ້ມາ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/execution.py:154
msgid "Requested boot drive \"{}\" doesn't exist or cannot be used."
msgstr "ໄດຣຟ໌ບູດ \"{}\" ທີ່ຮ້ອງຂໍບໍ່ມີຢູ່ ຫຼື ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ງານໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:189
msgid "/boot file system"
msgstr "ລະບົບໄຟລ໌ /boot"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:330
#, python-format
msgid ""
"RAID sets that contain '%(desc)s' must have one of the following raid "
"levels: %(raid_level)s."
msgstr ""
"ຊຸດ RAID ທີ່ມີ '%(desc)s' ຕ້ອງມີໜຶ່ງໃນລະດັບ RAID ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້: %(raid_level)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:338
#, python-format
msgid ""
"RAID sets that contain '%(desc)s' must have one of the following metadata "
"versions: %(metadata_versions)s."
msgstr ""
"ຊຸດ RAID ທີ່ມີ '%(desc)s' ຕ້ອງມີໜຶ່ງໃນເວີຊັນ metadata ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້: %(metadata_versions)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:346
#, python-format
msgid ""
"RAID sets that contain '%(desc)s' must have one of the following device "
"types: %(types)s."
msgstr "ຊຸດ RAID ທີ່ມີ '%(desc)s' ຕ້ອງມີໜຶ່ງໃນປະເພດອຸປະກອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້: %(types)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:362
#, python-format
msgid "%(name)s must have one of the following disklabel types: %(types)s."
msgstr "%(name)s ຕ້ອງມີໜຶ່ງໃນປະເພດປ້າຍຊື່ດິສກ໌ (disklabel) ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້: %(types)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:374
#, python-format
msgid "%(desc)s cannot be of type %(type)s."
msgstr "%(desc)s ບໍ່ສາມາດເປັນປະເພດ %(type)s ໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:380
#, python-format
msgid "%(desc)s must be mounted on one of %(mountpoints)s."
msgstr "%(desc)s ຕ້ອງເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບໜຶ່ງໃນ %(mountpoints)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:392
#, python-format
msgid "%(desc)s must be between %(min)d and %(max)d MB in size"
msgstr "%(desc)s ຕ້ອງມີຂະໜາດລະຫວ່າງ %(min)d ຫາ %(max)d MB"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:398
#, python-format
msgid "%(desc)s must not be smaller than %(min)dMB."
msgstr "%(desc)s ຕ້ອງບໍ່ນ້ອຍກວ່າ %(min)dMB."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:407
#, python-format
msgid "%(desc)s must not be larger than %(max)dMB."
msgstr "%(desc)s ຕ້ອງບໍ່ໃຫຍ່ກວ່າ %(max)dMB."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:425
#, python-format
msgid "%(desc)s must be within the first %(max_end)s of the disk."
msgstr "%(desc)s ຕ້ອງຢູ່ພາຍໃນ %(max_end)s ທຳອິດຂອງດິສກ໌."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:435
#, python-format
msgid "%s must be on a primary partition."
msgstr "%s ຕ້ອງຢູ່ໃນພາຕິຊັນຫຼັກ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:523
msgid ""
"Boot loader stage1 device cannot be on an iSCSI disk which is not configured "
"in iBFT."
msgstr ""
"ອຸປະກອນຕົວໂຫຼດບູດລະດັບ 1 ບໍ່ສາມາດຢູ່ໃນດິສກ໌ iSCSI ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນ iBFT."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:579
#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:699
#, python-format
msgid "%s cannot be on an encrypted block device."
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ສາມາດຢູ່ໃນອຸປະກອນບລັອກທີ່ເຂົ້າລະຫັດໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:651
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(bootloader_stage2_description)s cannot be on an iSCSI disk which is not "
"configured in iBFT."
msgstr ""
"%(bootloader_stage2_description)s ບໍ່ສາມາດຢູ່ໃນດິສກ໌ iSCSI ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນ iBFT."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/base.py:658
#, python-format
msgid "%(desc)s cannot be of type %(type)s"
msgstr "%(desc)s ບໍ່ສາມາດເປັນປະເພດ %(type)s"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/grub2.py:487
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(deviceName)s may not have enough space for grub2 to embed core.img when "
"using the %(fsType)s file system on %(deviceType)s"
msgstr ""
"%(deviceName)s ອາດຈະບໍ່ມີພື້ນທີ່ພຽງພໍສຳລັບ grub2 ໃນການຝັງ core.img ເມື່ອໃຊ້ລະບົບໄຟລ໌ %"
"(fsType)s ໃນ %(deviceType)s"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/grub2.py:526
#, python-format
msgid ""
"boot loader stage2 device %(stage2dev)s is on a multi-disk array, but boot "
"loader stage1 device %(stage1dev)s is not. A drive failure in %(stage2dev)s "
"could render the system unbootable."
msgstr ""
"ອຸປະກອນຕົວໂຫຼດບູດລະດັບ 2 %(stage2dev)s ຢູ່ໃນອາເຣແບບຫຼາຍດິສກ໌, ແຕ່ອຸປະກອນຕົວໂຫຼດບູດລະດັບ 1 %"
"(stage1dev)s ບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່. ຖ້າດິສກ໌ໃນ %(stage2dev)s ເພພັງອາດຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ລະບົບບໍ່ສາມາດບູດໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/bootloader/grub2.py:533
#, python-format
msgid ""
"boot loader stage2 device %(stage2dev)s is on a multi-disk array, but boot "
"loader stage1 device %(stage1dev)s is not part of this array. The stage1 "
"boot loader will only be installed to a single drive."
msgstr ""
"ອຸປະກອນຕົວໂຫຼດບູດລະດັບ 2 %(stage2dev)s ຢູ່ໃນອາເຣແບບຫຼາຍດິສກ໌, ແຕ່ອຸປະກອນຕົວໂຫຼດບູດລະດັບ 1 %"
"(stage1dev)s ບໍ່ໄດ້ເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງອາເຣນີ້. ຕົວໂຫຼດບູດລະດັບ 1 ຈະຖືກຕິດຕັ້ງໃສ່ດິສກ໌ດຽວເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

