msgstr "ເຊີບເວີ NTP:"

#: pyanaconda/ntp.py:92
msgid "not configured"
msgstr "ຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າ"

#: pyanaconda/input_checking.py:548
msgid "Full name cannot contain colon characters"
msgstr "ຊື່ເຕັມບໍ່ສາມາດມີຕົວອັກສອນຈ້ຳສອງເມັດ (colon)"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:79
#, python-format
msgid "%(productName)s %(productVersion)s installation"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕັ້ງ %(productName)s %(productVersion)s"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:148
#, python-format
msgid "%(productName)s %(productVersion)s installation on host %(name)s"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕັ້ງ %(productName)s %(productVersion)s ຢູ່ເທິງໂຮສ %(name)s"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:167
#, python-format
msgid "Attempting to connect to vnc client on host %s..."
msgstr "ກຳລັງພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາ vnc client ຢູ່ເທິງໂຮສ %s..."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:181
msgid "Connected!"
msgstr "ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ແລ້ວ!"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:184
msgid "Will try to connect again in 15 seconds..."
msgstr "ຈະພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໃໝ່ໃນອີກ 15 ວິນາທີ..."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:191
#, python-format
msgid "Giving up attempting to connect after %d try!\n"
msgid_plural "Giving up attempting to connect after %d tries!\n"
msgstr[0] "ຍົກເລີກການພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫຼັງຈາກລອງໄປແລ້ວ %d ຄັ້ງ!\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:199
msgid "Attempting to start vncconfig"
msgstr "ກຳລັງພະຍາຍາມເລີ່ມ vncconfig"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:212
#, python-format
msgid "Please manually connect your vnc client to %s to begin the install."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ vnc client ຂອງທ່ານຫາ %s ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງເພື່ອເລີ່ມການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:214
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Please manually connect your vnc client to IP-ADDRESS:%s to begin the "
"install. Switch to the shell (Ctrl-B 2) and run 'ip addr' to find the IP-"
"ADDRESS."
msgstr ""
"ກະລຸນາເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ vnc client ຂອງທ່ານຫາ IP-ADDRESS:%s ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງເພື່ອເລີ່ມການຕິດຕັ້ງ. ປ່ຽນໄປທີ່ "
"shell (Ctrl-B 2) ແລ້ວຣັນ 'ip addr' ເພື່ອຊອກຫາ IP-ADDRESS."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:219
msgid "Starting VNC..."
msgstr "ກຳລັງເລີ່ມ VNC..."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:256
msgid "The VNC server is now running."
msgstr "ເຊີບເວີ VNC ກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກຢູ່."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:260
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"You chose to connect to a listening vncviewer. \n"
"This does not require a password to be set.  If you \n"
"set a password, it will be used in case the connection \n"
"to the vncviewer is unsuccessful\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"ທ່ານເລືອກທີ່ຈະເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາ vncviewer ທີ່ກຳລັງລໍຖ້າການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່. \n"
"ນີ້ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຕັ້ງລະຫັດຜ່ານ. ຖ້າທ່ານ \n"
"ຕັ້ງລະຫັດຜ່ານ, ມັນຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ \n"
"ຫາ vncviewer ບໍ່ສຳເລັດ\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:265
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"WARNING!!! VNC server running with NO PASSWORD!\n"
"You can use the vncpassword=PASSWORD boot option\n"
"if you would like to secure the server.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"ຄຳເຕືອນ!!! ເຊີບເວີ VNC ກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກໂດຍບໍ່ມີລະຫັດຜ່ານ!\n"
"ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກບູດ vncpassword=PASSWORD\n"
"ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການເຮັດໃຫ້ເຊີບເວີປອດໄພ.\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:269
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"You chose to execute vnc with a password. \n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"ທ່ານເລືອກທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ vnc ພ້ອມກັບລະຫັດຜ່ານ. \n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:271
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"Unknown Error.  Aborting. \n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດທີ່ບໍ່ຮູ້ຈັກ. ກຳລັງຍົກເລີກ. \n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:293
msgid ""
"VNC password must be six to eight characters long.\n"
"Please enter a new one, or leave blank for no password."
msgstr ""
"ລະຫັດຜ່ານ VNC ຕ້ອງມີຄວາມຍາວແຕ່ 6 ຫາ 8 ຕົວອັກສອນ.\n"
"ກະລຸນາປ້ອນລະຫັດໃໝ່ ຫຼື ປະຫວ່າງໄວ້ຖ້າບໍ່ຕ້ອງການລະຫັດຜ່ານ."

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:272
msgid "Unable to find /bin/bash to execute!  Not starting shell."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຊອກຫາ /bin/bash ເພື່ອປະມວນຜົນ! ຈະບໍ່ເລີ່ມການເຮັດວຽກຂອງ shell."

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:289
msgid "Rescue"
msgstr "ກູ້ຄືນ (Rescue)"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:296
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The rescue environment will now attempt to find your Linux installation and "
"mount it under the directory : %s.  You can then make any changes required "
"to your system.  Choose '1' to proceed with this step.\n"
"You can choose to mount your file systems read-only instead of read-write by "
"choosing '2'.\n"
"If for some reason this process does not work choose '3' to skip directly to "
"a shell.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບກູ້ຄືນຈະພະຍາຍາມຊອກຫາການຕິດຕັ້ງ Linux ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ມັນໄວ້ພາຍໃຕ້ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ: %s. ຈາກນັ້"
"ນທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງສິ່ງຕ່າງໆທີ່ຈຳເປັນຕໍ່ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານໄດ້. ເລືອກ '1' ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້.\n"
"ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ລະບົບໄຟລ໌ຂອງທ່ານແບບອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ (read-only) ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນແບບອ່ານ-ຂຽນ "
"(read-write) ໂດຍການເລືອກ '2'.\n"
"ຫາກຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້ໃຊ້ການບໍ່ໄດ້ຍ້ອນເຫດຜົນບາງຢ່າງ ໃຫ້ເລືອກ '3' ເພື່ອຂ້າມໄປໃຊ້ shell ໂດຍກົງ.\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:308
msgid "Continue"
msgstr "ດຳເນີນການຕໍ່"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:309
msgid "Read-only mount"
msgstr "ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ແບບອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:310
msgid "Skip to shell"
msgstr "ຂ້າມໄປຫາ shell"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:311
msgid "Quit (Reboot)"
msgstr "ອອກ (ເລີ່ມລະບົບໃໝ່)"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:408
msgid "Rescue Shell"
msgstr "Shell ກູ້ຄືນ"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:418
#, python-format
msgid "Run %s to unmount the system when you are finished."
msgstr "ຣັນ %s ເພື່ອຍົກເລີກການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ລະບົບເມື່ອທ່ານເຮັດວຽກສຳເລັດແລ້ວ."

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:419
msgid ""
"When finished, please exit from the shell and your system will reboot.\n"
msgstr "ເມື່ອສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ກະລຸນາອອກຈາກ shell ແລະ ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານຈະເລີ່ມໃໝ່.\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:430
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your system has been mounted under %(mountpoint)s.\n"
"\n"
"If you would like to make the root of your system the root of the active "
"system, run the command:\n"
"\n"
"\tchroot %(mountpoint)s\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານຖືກເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໄວ້ພາຍໃຕ້ %(mountpoint)s.\n"
"\n"
"ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການເຮັດໃຫ້ຮາກ (root) ຂອງລະບົບທ່ານ ກາຍເປັນຮາກຂອງລະບົບທີ່ກຳລັງໃຊ້ງານຢູ່, ໃຫ້ຣັນຄຳສັ່"
"ງ:\n"
"\n"
"\tchroot %(mountpoint)s\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:442
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"An error occurred trying to mount some or all of your system: {message}\n"
"\n"
"Some of it may be mounted under {path}."
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນການພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ບາງສ່ວນ ຫຼື ທັງໝົດຂອງລະບົບຂອງທ່ານ: {message}\n"
"\n"
"ບາງສ່ວນອາດຖືກເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໄວ້ພາຍໃຕ້ {path}."

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:454
msgid "You don't have any Linux partitions.\n"
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ມີພາທິຊັນ Linux ໃດໆ.\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:460
msgid "Not mounting the system.\n"
msgstr "ຈະບໍ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ລະບົບ.\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:474
#, python-format
msgid "Please press %s to get a shell"
msgstr "ກະລຸນາກົດ %s ເພື່ອເຂົ້າຫາ shell"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:491
msgid "Root Selection"
msgstr "ການເລືອກ Root"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:517
msgid "The following installations were discovered on your system."
msgstr "ພົບການຕິດຕັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນລະບົບຂອງທ່ານ."

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:83
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(product_name)s requires %(needed_ram)s MB of memory to install, but you "
"only have %(total_ram)s MB on this machine.\n"
msgstr ""
"%(product_name)s ຕ້ອງການ %(needed_ram)s MB ເພື່ອຕິດຕັ້ງ, ແຕ່ທ່ານມີພຽງແຕ່ %(total_ram)s "
"MB ໃນເຄື່ອງນີ້.\n"

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:85
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The %(product_name)s graphical installer requires %(needed_ram)s MB of "
"memory, but you only have %(total_ram)s MB.\n"
msgstr ""
"ຕົວຕິດຕັ້ງແບບກຣາຟິກ %(product_name)s ຕ້ອງການໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ %(needed_ram)s MB, ແຕ່ທ່ານມີພຽງ "
"%(total_ram)s MB.\n"

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:88
msgid ""
"\n"
"Press [Enter] to reboot your system.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"ກົດ [Enter] ເພື່ອເລີ່ມລະບົບໃໝ່.\n"

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:90
msgid "Not enough RAM"
msgstr "RAM ບໍ່ພຽງພໍ"

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:91
msgid ""
" Try the text mode installer by running:\n"
"\n"
"'/usr/bin/liveinst -T'\n"
"\n"
" from a root terminal."
msgstr ""
" ລອງໃຊ້ຕົວຕິດຕັ້ງແບບຂໍ້ຄວາມ (text mode) ໂດຍການຣັນ:\n"
"\n"
"'/usr/bin/liveinst -T'\n"
"\n"
" ຈາກເທີມິນໍຣາກ (root terminal)."

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:93
msgid " Starting text mode."
msgstr " ກຳລັງເລີ່ມໂໝດຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:130
msgid "The installation cannot continue and the system will be rebooted"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕັ້ງບໍ່ສາມາດດຳເນີນການຕໍ່ໄດ້ ແລະ ລະບົບຈະຖືກເລີ່ມໃໝ່"

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:131
msgid "Press ENTER to continue"
msgstr "ກົດ ENTER ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່"

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:277
#, python-format
msgid "Please ssh install@%s to begin the install."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາ ssh install@%s ເພື່ອເລີ່ມການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:279
msgid "Please ssh install@HOSTNAME to continue installation."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາ ssh install@HOSTNAME ເພື່ອຕິດຕັ້ງຕໍ່."

#: pyanaconda/display.py:321
msgid "Graphical installation is not available. Starting text mode."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ການຕິດຕັ້ງແບບກຣາຟິກໄດ້. ກຳລັງເລີ່ມໂໝດຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#: pyanaconda/display.py:329
msgid ""
"Text mode provides a limited set of installation options. It does not offer "
"custom partitioning for full control over the disk layout. Would you like to "
"use VNC mode instead?"
msgstr ""
"ໂໝດຂໍ້ຄວາມມີຕົວເລືອກການຕິດຕັ້ງທີ່ຈຳກັດ. ມັນບໍ່ມີການແບ່ງພາທິຊັນແບບກຳນົດເອງເພື່ອຄວບຄຸມຮູບແບບດິສຢ່າງເຕັມສ່ວ"
"ນ. ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ໂໝດ VNC ແທນບໍ່?"

#: pyanaconda/display.py:372
msgid ""
"X was unable to start on your machine. Would you like to start VNC to "
"connect to this computer from another computer and perform a graphical "
"installation or continue with a text mode installation?"
msgstr ""
"X ບໍ່ສາມາດເລີ່ມເຮັດວຽກໃນເຄື່ອງຂອງທ່ານໄດ້. ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເລີ່ມ VNC ເພື່ອເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາຄອມພິວເຕີເຄື່ອງນີ້ຈາກຄອ"
"ມພິວເຕີເຄື່ອງອື່ນ ແລະ ດຳເນີນການຕິດຕັ້ງແບບກຣາຟິກ ຫຼື ຈະຕິດຕັ້ງຕໍ່ດ້ວຍໂໝດຂໍ້ຄວາມ?"

